Titolo: Elemental Gimmick Gear

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: Elemental Gimmick Gear (エレメンタルギミックギア) is an action role-playing game for the Sega Dreamcast console.  Elemental Gimmick Gear uses hand-drawn art in an overhead view during exploration, then switches to 3D graphics during boss battles. It was developed by Birthday and published by Hudson Soft in Japan and Vatical Entertainment in the United States.

Genere: Action role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
